messages.content: It would be amazing if you could help us promote this new Alexa skill for visually and reading impaired people. Simply say Alexa enable Talking Newspaper and then Alexa play talking newspaper and funally Alexa play the herald. Thank you if you can help us.

share.share_text: "Alexa Enable Talking Newspaper" that's all you have to say to access talking newspapers use the evaluation form at www.printtoaudio.org to let us know what we can improve. #alexa #talkingnewspaper #blind

messages.content: It would be so amazing if you would share or like this post. As an Audio Ambassador you can help us reach more potential reading and visually impaired listeners. Our volunteer readers put the work in each day. Can you help?
